name: Always take the bright side of life
description:
"Some things in life are bad
They can really make you mad
Other things just make you swear and curse
When you're chewing on life's gristle
Don't grumble, give a whistle
And this'll help things turn out for the best

And always take the bright side of life"

This scratchboard was inspired by a flash tatto from 404tearzzz.

Original scratchboard: 12 x 12 cm
PNG | 5000 x 5000 px | 2021
